DESCRIPTION:3rd Annual Tartan Twilight 5k Glow Run/Walk presented by Radfo
 rd University in Roanoke (Radford \nUniversity Carilion). The purpose of 
 the Tartan Twilight 5k is to promote student and community health \nand w
 ell-being\, encourage connection to the outdoors and the Roanoke City Gre
 enways\, and support the \nStudent Wellness initiatives at Radford Univer
 sity in Roanoke. The proposed course for the 5K is the \nRivers Edge Nort
 h Roanoke River Greenway with the start/finish line in the green open spa
 ce at Rivers Edge North. Pre-race \nactivities (e.g. on-site registration
 \, participation packet pickup\, etc.) starts at 5pm with the official st
 art \ntime of the 5k glow run/walk at 6:10pm. Post-race activities will s
 tart approximately 8:30pm and include \nawards presentation and music. ht
 tps://www.roanokeva.gov/calendar.aspx?EID=8522
