DESCRIPTION:This is a fundraiser for the National Fallen Firefighters Foun
 dation in memoriam of 9/11.  Registrants climb the Wells Fargo Tower step
 s 5 times (22 stories x 5 = 110 stories\, the height of the World Trade C
 enters) to honor the sacrifices of fire\, police\, and EMS on 9/11.  Ther
 e is a very brief parade at the beginning of the event (from 12:10-12:15)
 where participants march around the building and then enter the building 
 to begin the climb. https://www.roanokeva.gov/calendar.aspx?EID=6610
