DESCRIPTION:Kick-off your race season in great weather conditions at the s
 tart of summer!  With expansive views of the Blue Ridge Mountains\, athle
 tes are sure to enjoy all that Roanoke has to offer during the inaugural 
 year of Carilion Clinic’s IRONMAN 70.3 Virginia’s Blue Ridge.  There's a 
 reason Roanoke has been coined America's East Coast Mountain Biking Capit
 al! Virginia has a wide array of metro-mountain adventures and hundreds o
 f miles of hiking trails\, including the world-famous Appalachian Trail! 
